{"tid":1133804,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係成日都好攰","createTime":"2019-05-01T10:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T11:01:33.000Z","uid":185909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ea4d3fb2b227270d4e6ac4e3f24b423eafad2e","tid":1133804,"uid":185909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"男，未夠26歲<br />\n<br />\n返寫字樓工作，一日返八至10個鐘， 8:30起身<br />\n返工間唔中要用腦，有時間就上下連登hea下<br />\n<br />\n運動比較少做，一星期一次，只係出少少汗<br />\n瞓覺大概7-8個鐘<br />\n但長期都處於好攰嘅狀態(都好多年)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一放工就攰到想即刻返屋企<br />\n放工一若人去到九點幾十點就攰到好辛苦<br />\n種攰係連野都唔想講<br />\n冇精力諗嘢同做嘢(如煮飯)<br />\n好容易會有暈嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n之前睇中醫佢話我係虛寒體質<br />\n身體狀態感覺好似阿伯咁<br />\n連個樣睇落都好憔悴<br />\n想知有咩方法改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567dd7d674dc79fe92ec891c23fd935a2d66fe3e","tid":1133804,"uid":52474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"打少啲飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fd865c990341cd03d7d83f8f657035fe9e97fa","tid":1133804,"uid":24368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"每日瞓十幾個鐘都仲係覺得好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e326b4e064980c9293baa3aaa72e4bcb8e12db4","tid":1133804,"uid":160268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"做gym 有朋友同你一樣case<br />\n<br />\n做咗年鬆性格都變開朗埋"},{"pid":"8df8a770de3f36474e6c01fa5aafb418f3c4f3aa","tid":1133804,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"基因問題<br />\n<br />\n無乜野既 係個人廢啲姐"},{"pid":"f5760276fd5a5331ed3107f6e1497d226fc635a7","tid":1133804,"uid":185909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98fd865c990341cd03d7d83f8f657035fe9e97fa","tid":1133804,"uid":24368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"每日瞓十幾個鐘都仲係覺得好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/